product_array.name: AUTOMOBILI LAMBORGHINI ICONIC PADDED GILET
product_array.description: Automobili Lamborghini Iconic Padded Gilet with recycled wadding and heat-sealed seams. Two side pockets, customised with a rubberised shield logo on the chest. Regular fit. Main fabric composition: 100% nylon. Lining: 100% polyester. Padding: 100% recycled polyester.

product_array.name: 2 IN 1 JACKET FOR MEN - DESCENTE X AUTOMOBILI LAMBORGHINI
product_array.description:
The 2in1 down vest plus the padding jacket gives you the option to wear in versatile conditions. The vest uses 3L material to keep the main body part dry at all times. Simultaneously, the water-repellant inner jacket insulated with PRIMALOFT uses DESCENTE’s unique HEAT NAVI technology, which efficiently converts light into heat and provides active heat retention. Product details include carbon tape and back lining.

Main features:
Heat Control 5.0
PRIMALOFT
SEAM SEAL
GOOSE DOWN
HEAT NAVI
